		Excerpts from &amp;ldquo;Don&amp;rsquo;t let the RAT bite you,&amp;rdquo; Mikael Croholm, ITC International, from InfraMation Conference&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;
		Excerpts from &amp;ldquo;How to Guarantee Your Failure as an Infrared Thermographer,&amp;rdquo; Ron Lucier, ITC instructor, from InfraMation Conference&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;
		Excerpts from &amp;ldquo;A Primer on Infrared Thermography V2.&amp;rdquo; Gary L. Orlove and Robert P. Madding, ITC instructors&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;
		Excerpts from &amp;ldquo;Emissivity Measurement and Temperature Correction Accuracy Considerations,&amp;rdquo; Robert P. Madding, ITC instructor&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;About the author:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
