&lt;P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal&gt;&lt;SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman','serif'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA"&gt;&lt;IMG id=_x0000_i1031 src="http://www.thermoteknix.com/content/english/stories/lcross_nasa_moon_mission/images/small_moon.jpg" width=223 height=192&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;EM&gt;&lt;SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Verdana','sans-serif'; FONT-SIZE: 7.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA"&gt;Thermal Image of Earth - taken with MIRICLE TB2-30 Camera &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/EM&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;
