            <title>Primer on FLIR infrared camera/thermal imager</title>
            <description>&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN id=vidDescRemain style="DISPLAY: inline"&gt;The InfraCAM infrared camera/thermal imager from FLIR is low cost and high quality. It is ideal for electricians, facility managers, energy auditors, substation/troubleshooting/customer service inspection crews, or anyone who wants to do a better job with their predictive and facility maintenance programs.&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;Access this 2-minute, 52-second video by clicking on the link below.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;
