            <title>Infrared thermal imaging in the utility industry</title>
            <description>&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN id=vidDescRemain style="DISPLAY: inline"&gt;This video shows FLIR cameras in the field and why infrared thermal imaging has become a key tool for predictive maintenance programs for utility firms everywhere.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN style="DISPLAY: inline"&gt;Access this 3-minute, 33-second video by clicking on the link below.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/infrared_thermography/~4/lEp39W_iqlI" height="1" width="1" alt=""/&gt;</description>
