&lt;P&gt;When does it make sense to combine dynamic signal analysis and image indications of machinery health into a single device? We invite your feedback. Please e-mail your responses to &lt;A href="mailto:ray.garvey@emersonprocess.com"&gt;ray.garvey@emersonprocess.com&lt;/A&gt;.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/infrared_thermography/~4/nHLOajdKU8U" height="1" width="1" alt=""/&gt;</description>
