            <title>Snell Group launches online forum for thermographers</title>
            <description>&lt;P class=MsoPlainText style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"&gt;&lt;SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial"&gt;The Snell Group on May 8 announced the launch of IRTalk.com, a new online community and learning forum dedicated to professional thermographers and the world of thermal imaging.&lt;?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P class=MsoPlainText style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"&gt;&lt;SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P class=MsoPlainText style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"&gt;&lt;SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial"&gt;This new service from The Snell Group both updates and expands one of the most popular message boards in the industry. IRTalk.com debuts with four individual forums dedicated to a specific area of thermography: Applications, IR Classroom, Equipment Talk and Classifieds. Registration is free and open to everyone, enabling users to participate and respond to any of the online discussions.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P class=MsoPlainText style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"&gt;&lt;SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P class=MsoPlainText style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"&gt;&lt;SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial"&gt;Among the many features, members will find improved message formatting options with custom fonts, text sizing, signatures and avatars; enhanced search capabilities for posts by topic, date and author; customizable e-mail notifications for all message posts and replies and optional RSS feeds for individual messages, entire boards, or even search results.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P class=MsoPlainText style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"&gt;&lt;SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P class=MsoPlainText style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"&gt;&lt;SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial"&gt;IRTalk.com is an online community of infrared professionals that welcomes everyone regardless of their equipment preference, training, experience or applications. Whether you are a maintenance technician, reliability engineer, electrical contractor, building inspector, weatherization professional, infrared service provider or just want to know more about thermography, IRTalk.com is the place to learn from those who are active in the industry.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;
