&lt;P class=MsoPlainText style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"&gt;&lt;SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial"&gt;The Snell Group is the leading provider of asset reliability and efficiency solutions using infrared technology and motor circuit analysis, enabling organizations to increase uptime and save money while improving safety. &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P class=MsoPlainText style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"&gt;&lt;SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P class=MsoPlainText style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"&gt;&lt;SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"&gt;Assisting organizations at all stages of their reliability program, The Snell Group offers clients audits, program assessments, consulting services, training, mentoring, inspections and knowledge resources such as IRTalk.com. The company is vendor neutral and supports all types of infrared and motor circuit analysis equipment, regardless of manufacturer. &lt;SPAN style="COLOR: black"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/infrared_thermography/~4/5oH4vjJZUQM" height="1" width="1" alt=""/&gt;</description>
