&lt;P class=reference&gt;2) See U.S. Patent 6,078,874, Column 13, lines 33 to 58. &lt;/P&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/infrared_thermography/~4/bFspkEBN79s" height="1" width="1" alt=""/&gt;</description>
